Favored Enemy					KEY:Eldeen Ranger ~ Favored Enemy						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.Class Feature.Eldeen Ranger Class Feature.SpecialQuality																DESC:At 4th level, an Eldeen ranger gains a favored enemy. This ability works just like the ranger's favored enemy ability, and it allows the Eldeen ranger to increase the bonus against one of his favored enemies as if he had just gained another favored enemy from his ranger class.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.76
