Monastic Training																CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MonkBonusFeat.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary								VISIBLE:YES	!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT, Monastic Training							DESC:You are part of an order that combines the monastic discipline of the monk class with another form of training.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														MULT:YES	CHOOSE:CLASS|TYPE=Base|TYPE=PC							ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Monastic Training (%LIST)																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												BENEFIT:Pick one class. Taking levels in this class does not prevent you from taking monk levels. If you take levels in any other class, you lose your ability to progress as a monk as usual. If the selected class also has restricted advancement, such as the paladin class, taking monk levels does not prevent you from advancing in that class.
